title: The L Word Recap: 2.09  “Late, Later, Latent”
itunes:title: The L Word Recap: 2.09  “Late, Later, Latent”
description:
PANTS with Kate Moennig and Leisha Hailey

Produced by Melisa D. Monts and Diamond MPrint Productions

Edited by Diane Kang 

 

Kate and Leisha talk “Euphoria” and an unfashionable trip to see goats. They then recap the ninth episode of Season 2 of “The L Word”.
